{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778523466861,"sessionID":"ses_1e7be980dffel3BsH5wKu3Kc5K","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"chatcmpl-tool-b21a4319040f8b0c","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/runner/work/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/__issue_context__.json"},"output":"<path>/home/runner/work/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/__issue_context__.json</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: {\n2:   \"body\": \"**Preferred term label:**\\ncarotid artery intima–media region\\n\\n**Synonyms**\\ncarotid intima–media PMID:[39416432](https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/39416432/)\\n\\n\\n**Definition (free text, please give PubMed ID)**\\nA region of the carotid artery wall composed of the tunica intima and tunica media.\\n\\n**Parent term (use https://www.ebi.ac.uk/ols/ontologies/uberon)**\\n'[multi-tissue structure](http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_0000481)'\\n'part of' some '[carotid artery segment](http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_0005396)'\\n'has part' some '[tunica intima](http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_0002523)'\\n'has part' some '[tunica media](http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_0002522)'\\n\\n**DisjointWith**\\n'[tunica adventitia of blood vessel](http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_0005734)'\\n\\n**Your nano-attribution (ORCID)**\\nhttps://orcid.org/0000-0001-6677-8489\\n\\n**Reason for addition**\\nTerm needed for creating a term in OBA 'carotid intima-media thickness'\\n\\n\\n\",\n3:   \"comments\": [\n4:     {\n5:       \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAAidd87Sgjf2\",\n6:       \"author\": {\n7:         \"login\": \"aleixpuigb\"\n8:       },\n9:       \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n10:       \"body\": \"@dragon-ai-agent please, add this term. Disregard the part of 'reason for addition'.\",\n11:       \"createdAt\": \"2025-11-14T09:20:01Z\",\n12:       \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n13:       \"isMinimized\": false,\n14:       \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n15:       \"reactionGroups\": [],\n16:      